    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户旅程图，展示教练在LMS门户里从登录到查看训练进度的完整流程。核心场景是规划和记录单次训练。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User Journey: Plan & Log a Session",
        "Authentication",
        "Dashboard",
        "Planner",
        "Logger",
        "Progress"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我先确认一下结构：开头是认证环节，然后到Dashboard，接着进入Planner做计划，之后Logger里记录实际执行情况，最后Progress看数据。这样五个section对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Authentication",
        "section Dashboard",
        "section Planner",
        "section Logger",
        "section Progress"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，顺序没错。认证部分要包含2FA，因为教育平台有安全要求。Planner里要能添加训练动作和设置重复周期，Logger里需要关联到Education_LMS_Portal这个具体系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Enter credentials & 2FA",
        "Add exercises & recurrence",
        "Record actuals (Education_LMS_Portal)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主干：用户打开登录页、输入凭证和2FA，系统验证后重定向。然后用户在Dashboard查看下一个计划好的训练，或者点击\"Plan new session\"创建新的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Open login page",
        "Enter credentials & 2FA",
        "Backend validates, redirects",
        "View next planned session",
        "Click \"Plan new session\""
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Planner部分再细化一下：添加训练动作、设置重复规则，然后保存计划。Logger这边要体现\"打开已计划的训练\"这个入口，因为用户是从计划列表里选一条来执行的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Add exercises & recurrence",
        "Save planned session",
        "Open planned session"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已加上。Logger里我放了三个步骤：打开计划好的训练、在Education_LMS_Portal记录实际完成情况、标记为完成。最后Progress部分用户打开进度仪表盘看图表和连续记录。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Open planned session",
        "Record actuals (Education_LMS_Portal)",
        "Mark as complete",
        "Open Progress Dashboard",
